description.plain: Asylum Party is a French band founded in 1985 in Courbevoie by Thierry Sobezyk (bass, vocals) and Philippe Planchon (guitar, vocals), later joined by Pascale Macé (keyboards), Asylum Party was part of the so-called Touching Pop movement together with Mary Goes Round and Little Nemo. They disbanded in 1991.

songs.embed_content: Read “The Sabbath” by Asylum Party on Genius
songs.title: The Sabbath
songs.lyrics:
White flying horse
Sings the magic
His dream takes you
Back to the beginning

The sorceress
Is black widow
She starts to dance
With fire in her hands

Moonless night
Ninety years old
A young elf
Between darkness and dawn

Voices and drums
All demons are there
Frenzy and moves
It's the sweetest nightmare
Join the pagan mass
Lost souls are free now

songs.embed_content: Read “La Nuit” by Asylum Party on Genius
songs.title: La Nuit
songs.lyrics:
Pourquoi cette grimace sur ton visage?
Chaque fois que tu essayes de sourire
On dirait qu'en toi s'ouvre une cage
Quel animal va-t-il en sortir?

Tu as prononcé les mots mortels
Qui rendent éphémère l'instant présent
Tu as rampé hors de ton linceul
Pour mieux plonger dans le fleuve du temps

Ecoute les voix de la nuit
Hurler la faim infinie
Maintenant tu vois dans la nuit
Maintenant tes griffes sont sorties

songs.embed_content: Read “Pictures” by Asylum Party on Genius
songs.title: Pictures
songs.lyrics:
Something broke one day
And he stopped talking
Something broke in the head
Young child stopped looking out

Something talks away
Some shrieks of laughter
Besounding in the air
An inner call to be loved

Take off those pictures
That make me cry, that kill me

Something comes too late
Lower than whispers
Something has come too late
The mad desire to be here again

album.name: What Will You Learn

songs.lyrics:
I see you playing on the ground
I need you driving through the town
I heard you laughing in dismay
Now I have to prevent your extend

Don't be surprised, I told you
You're here to cry, I told you

What colour do you think this day
Will bring out in my tidy head?
I hope this won't take me too down
Now you speak "will you take a dream cloud"?

Don't be surprised, I told you
You're here to cry, I told you

songs.full_title: Sweetness... Of Pain by Asylum Party
songs.title: Sweetness... Of Pain

annotatable.link_title: Sweetness... Of Pain by Asylum Party
annotatable.title: Sweetness... Of Pain

songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Mother's arms in young days
Black promises white betrayals
Just to kill faith
Father's eye crucified
Love in a great bed of lament
Ignoring tears

[Chorus]
Taste the sweetness of pain
Pain
Drink all the pain
In your veins

[Verse 2]
Who's this man looking sad?
Walking slowly speaking lonely
Singing old prayers
To the wind
Who's this child of desire?
Captured by his own freedom
Ignoring his faith

[Chorus]
Taste the sweetness of pain
Pain
Drink all the pain
In your veins

[Instrumental]

[Chorus]
Taste the sweetness of pain
Pain
Drink all the pain
In your veins

Taste the sweetness of pain
Pain
Drink all the pain
In your veins

songs.embed_content: Read “White Light” by Asylum Party on Genius
songs.title: White Light
songs.lyrics:
Many times I pray to draw my own face
Many times I stay lost back in past
Trying to find again the childhood full of reason
Don't you call my name
I heard a voice off

Round and round
We walk to final line
Will you consider me dying
Over white light
Over white light

Sometimes I dream I change the seasons
Sometimes I feel sunrise's coming
As the sound of a weary rain will die inside me
Won't you call my name
It's everything I know
Everything I know
Everything

Round and round
We walk to final line
Will you consider me dying
Over white light
Over white light
Over white light

A gentle and bright love is so hard to find
And so far in a corridor, a baby toy waits

songs.lyrics:
Alone we talk of time
Alone we talk of past days
And I don't recall why
We never talk in darkness

Alone we watch the sky
For as long as we can stay
But I still cannot find
The place where we used to play

Every moment of my life with you
Still lives in your eyes
And I always will look after you
And your smile

Alone we talk of time
Alone we talk of past days
The weather turns out fine
We can hope for happiness

Every moment of my life with you
Still lives in your eyes
And I always will look after you
And your smile

Every moment of my life with you
Still lives in your eyes
And I always will look after you
Every moment of my life with you

annotatable.link_title: Old Dreams Are Not Innocent by Asylum Party
annotatable.title: Old Dreams Are Not Innocent

songs.lyrics:
So sad
To live here
To get nothing
By a grey Sunday
Someone was born
Something ended

Old dreams of you
Old dreams satisfy

So dirty
Looking at old ages
Looking at madness

How much time
Before calling
Mother's help

Old dreams of you
Old dreams satisfy
Old dreams are not innocent
So sad
To live here
To get nothing

By a grey Sunday
Something’s ended
Someone has grown up

songs.title: Madhouse Grass
songs.lyrics:
Hates
Our belly waits
For shiny stars
Then
I'll find myself
Dry as a stone

Ice falls over our napes
Green ice falls
And I don't give a fuck, my lord

We eat the madhouse grass
To stay young
We eat the madhouse grass
To stay

Friends
We could remain
In such a park
May I spend these days
Around the crags

Ice falls over our napes
Green ice falls
And I don't give a fuck, my lord

We eat the madhouse grass
To stay young
We eat the madhouse grass
To stay young
We eat the madhouse grass
To stay

Basically cold
Need something to hold
Before I get old

annotatable.title: Le Temps Des Serpents

songs.lyrics:
Les serpents animés par le rythme
Déroulent leurs anneaux
Et glissent sur ta peau

Le vertige te prend devant l'abîme
Mais tu ne voudras pas
T'éloigner d'un pas

Percussions
Souffle et sueur
Répercussions
A craindre sur le coeur

Du poison
Change ton humeur
Et la raison
Qui attend son heure

Dans le noir tu as perdu ton ombre
Soudain derrière toi
Il n'y a plus de voie

Loin sous toi tu sens la terre qui gronde
C'est déjà trop tard
La magie t'égare

Percussions
Souffle et sueur
Répercussions
A craindre sur le coeur

Du poison
Change ton humeur
Et la raison
Qui attend son heure

Souffle et sueur, souffle et sueur

annotatable.title: Un Sang D'Hier

songs.lyrics:
Je ne veux pas
Mourir sur le sable des regrets
En écoutant les vagues de l'âme
Balayer le rêve à jamais
Rivage amer

Que retenir
De cette image brève comme l'éclair
Sous le silence au désir
Se rompt le lien d'un sang d'hier
Incendiaire

Sans un regard
Les sages ont le droit de partir
Briser le jeu de miroirs
Tuer le reflet à venir
Faire l'avenir
Vers l'avenir

songs.lyrics:
Rien ne peut arrêter
Le train à jamais lancé
Mon âme est partie brûler

Demain il sera peut-être

Je prends un peu de bonheur

songs.lyrics:

Jump, but don't fall on your knife

Là, entre ciel et terre, il n'y a plus de voile

Walk over houses top

C'est la nuit et je veux je ne sais plus quoi
